94
00:06:52,774 --> 00:06:53,747
That's great.

95
00:06:54,121 --> 00:06:55,115
Then...

96
00:06:55,364 --> 00:06:57,317
This Sunday, let's have
a rematch with curry.

97
00:06:59,066 --> 00:07:00,287
A rematch with curry.

98
