110
00:08:19,595 --> 00:08:20,562
Yeah.

111
00:08:21,469 --> 00:08:23,620
Really? That's amazing.

112
00:08:23,622 --> 00:08:25,038
Amazing.

113
00:08:28,122 --> 00:08:31,060
Can you teach me how to make a lunchbox?

114
00:08:31,143 --> 00:08:32,566
Of course, I'll help you.

115
00:08:32,689 --> 00:08:35,015
I hope the boy will be happy with it.

116
00:08:45,548 --> 00:08:48,728
Wow, amazing.

117
00:08:49,951 --> 00:08:51,458
Yummy.

118
00:08:51,458 --> 00:08:52,758
Really?

119
00:08:53,611 --> 00:08:54,947
That's a relief.

120
00:09:06,146 --> 00:09:08,648
I never thought eating with someone

121
00:09:09,516 --> 00:09:11,518
would make me so happy.

122
00:09:14,183 --> 00:09:16,089
Back then, I never knew.

123
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:48,321
Tane, it's been a while.

124
00:09:48,347 --> 00:09:50,658
Yukata.

125
00:09:51,158 --> 00:09:53,426
Finally, we're going to make curry.
Curry.

126
00:09:53,472 --> 00:09:54,318
That's right.

127
00:09:55,060 --> 00:09:56,563
All right, let's go.

128
00:09:57,061 --> 00:10:02,948
(Daily Mart)
Curry...

129
00:10:02,958 --> 00:10:04,471
What's that song?

130
00:10:05,018 --> 00:10:06,372
It's the curry song!

131
00:10:06,456 --> 00:10:07,662
The curry song?

132
00:10:13,040 --> 00:10:14,414
Do you want to add sweet potatoes?

133
00:10:14,740 --> 00:10:15,991
Yes.

134
00:10:15,991 --> 00:10:17,951
Isn't it weird to add sweet potatoes?

135
00:10:19,986 --> 00:10:23,106
I once got sweet potatoes from
my landlord when I was making curry,

136
00:10:23,133 --> 00:10:25,091
