220
00:16:44,249 --> 00:16:45,227
All right...

221
00:16:46,065 --> 00:16:48,123
Thank you for the food.

222
00:17:00,888 --> 00:17:02,147
Yummy.

223
00:17:03,002 --> 00:17:04,757
Minoru, you're great at making curry.

224
00:17:05,921 --> 00:17:07,059
- No.
- Right?

225
00:17:07,182 --> 00:17:08,027
Yeah.

226
00:17:08,085 --> 00:17:09,894
You're a genius.

227
00:17:09,919 --> 00:17:12,932
No, I just followed
the instruction on the box.

228
00:17:12,932 --> 00:17:14,000
He's a genius, right?

229
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:14,834
Yeah.

230
00:17:15,023 --> 00:17:16,302
It's very good.

231
00:17:16,836 --> 00:17:18,604
Yummy.

232
00:17:21,102 --> 00:17:22,535
- It tastes good, right?
- Yeah.

233
00:17:24,453 --> 00:17:25,529
Can I more?

234
00:17:25,912 --> 00:17:26,961
You should ask, "Can I have more?"

235
00:17:26,961 --> 00:17:28,381
Pork really goes well with it.

236
00:17:28,641 --> 00:17:30,149
The sweet potato is good too.

237
00:17:30,149 --> 00:17:31,017
Really?

238
00:17:31,298 --> 00:17:32,569
How much more do you want?

239
00:17:32,702 --> 00:17:33,853
This much.

240
00:17:33,956 --> 00:17:35,154
What does that mean?

241
00:17:41,527 --> 00:17:43,763
I'm so full.

242
00:17:43,938 --> 00:17:44,997
So full, right?

243
00:17:45,286 --> 00:17:46,933
Try touching it.

244
00:17:47,381 --> 00:17:48,301
Where?

245
00:17:48,603 --> 00:17:49,969
Right.

246
00:17:50,009 --> 00:17:51,404
