256
00:18:28,722 --> 00:18:29,976
Oh, no.

257
00:18:30,910 --> 00:18:33,913
I didn't even eat anything
because I wanted to eat the curry.

258
00:18:35,634 --> 00:18:36,549
Curry.

259
00:18:37,532 --> 00:18:38,351
Curry.

260
00:18:38,905 --> 00:18:41,624
Please, I want some curry.
Give me some curry. Please.

261
00:18:41,624 --> 00:18:42,989
Tane, clean up the table.

262
00:18:42,989 --> 00:18:44,156
Okay.

263
00:18:53,515 --> 00:18:54,709
I'm sorry for that.

264
00:18:54,734 --> 00:18:56,002
It's all right.

265
00:18:56,164 --> 00:18:58,904
Yukata, just think of us as family.

266
00:18:58,938 --> 00:19:00,773
Treat this place like your home, OK?

267
00:19:06,987 --> 00:19:09,315
If we add water into this,
will it still work?

268
00:19:11,011 --> 00:19:14,587
