and watery curry. Oh, no.

269
00:19:14,736 --> 00:19:17,556
No, I don't want to eat bland curry.

270
00:19:17,766 --> 00:19:18,486
Right?

271
00:19:18,511 --> 00:19:19,730
Sorry, Dad.

272
00:19:20,192 --> 00:19:21,260
It's okay.

273
00:19:21,303 --> 00:19:22,461
In the fridge,

274
00:19:22,544 --> 00:19:24,544
