275
00:19:24,619 --> 00:19:26,224
Isn't it expensive?

276
00:19:26,421 --> 00:19:28,421
No, I got them from Hashida.

277
00:19:39,741 --> 00:19:41,280
See you later, then.

278
00:19:41,463 --> 00:19:42,187
Okay.

279
00:19:43,310 --> 00:19:44,450
Well.

